      • storeInvoked

        void storeInvoked(PersistingElement pe)
        Sent before a listened PersistingElement is stored in the data store. The stored(PersistingElement) is invoked afterwards if and only if the persisting element has changed.
        Parameters:
        pe - the listened PersistingElement

        Parameters:

        activatedColumnFamilies - the list of column families that were activated

      • activateInvoked

        void activateInvoked(PersistingElement pe,
                   Set<ColumnFamily<?>> columnFamiliesToBeActivated)
        Sent before a listened PersistingElement was activated from the data store. It may happen that activated(PersistingElement, Set) is not invoked afterwards e.g. in case this activation corresponds to an PersistingElement.activateIfNotAlready(String...) on an already activated persisting element.
        Parameters:
        pe - the listened PersistingElement
        columnFamiliesToBeActivated - the list of column families that are to be activated
